  <name>Pomodoro</name>
  <summary>A beautiful, distraction-free Pomodoro timer</summary>

  <description>
    <p>A minimal Pomodoro timer that stays out of your way and helps you stay in the zone. Single binary, no runtime dependencies, transparent borderless window with system tray integration.</p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Focus, Break, and Long Break cycle with configurable durations</li>
      <li>Dark and Light themes with adjustable window transparency</li>
      <li>Gentle tick sound during focus sessions to keep you aware of time</li>
      <li>Alarm sound on session completion with independent volume controls</li>
      <li>Mini mode — a compact floating timer that stays out of your way</li>
      <li>System tray integration — runs in the background</li>
      <li>HiDPI support with crisp vector rendering</li>
      <li>Keyboard shortcuts: Space (start/pause), R (reset), S (settings)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

